channel.title: I am back
channel.description:
I am back i had GCSE exams i have finished all my exams :D. I have not coded for 2 years now so i forgot a lot of shit lol.
I started mopar from 2006/2007 i miss them days, also the old status page was way way better. before most RSPS never use VPS or don't know what is VPS. now days if i looked at the status page i see most servers with VPS hosted thats good.
well now i got 3 weeks nothing to do so i am going to learn java
I am good with html & php, i work in a computer repair shop so i am pro at removing virus lol ;D
